{"tid":321732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 伊巴預告有「重大宣佈」","createTime":"2017-07-14T10:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T15:05:17.000Z","uid":19889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce27e0fd9044d8ef4ab0963754e432c6f97e35f","tid":321732,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=YAvEeCNUZkubvKx4iKnYcDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fc80c5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】今夏回復自由身的伊巴謙莫域，與經理人拉奧拿會面後預告，即將有「重大宣佈」向外公佈。<br />\n伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）去季效力曼聯期間，膝部的十字韌帶受到重創，4月便提早收咧養傷，紅魔一方亦因此而持觀望態度，未與伊巴續約，不過仍讓後者在卡寧頓訓練場接受復康治療。 據西班牙《馬卡報》報道，伊巴與經理人拉奧拿近日已經會面，並強調：「他很快便有新消息對外公佈，這絕對是一個重大決定。」醫療團隊最初預計伊巴需要來年1月才能復出，惟伊巴康復速度驚人，有望提早回到球場，引起多間球會注視。 其中，有傳美職聯勁旅洛杉磯銀河簽入伊巴，教練奧拉佛卻指出：「銀河的DNA本來就是吸引世界級球員加盟，我們一直都在尋找這些球員，但同時我們的政策是不評論不屬於銀河的球員。」 35歲的伊巴上季為曼聯在各項賽事射入28球，紅魔與其完約後，已找來愛華頓前鋒盧卡古填補鋒線的空缺。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E6%9C%89-%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-054810458--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%259C%2589-%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588-054810458--spt.html&d=YAvEeCNUZkubvKx4iKnYcDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=630dd4c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E6%9C%89-%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-054810458--spt.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇A-Z新系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48eb50acacceab6e324640b7821b28022e1359ed","tid":321732,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話晒都一代梟雄<br />\n希望唔係落草為寇去支超"},{"pid":"1c39386e3bc3edcb20c32e4386518ec83dd99211","tid":321732,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"等睇簽番曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6fa09fcbcf7e4e958e6cfd5e5e44f8705d3061","tid":321732,"uid":9145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc61ddcbb52f1b3476bc010c1c4c815500e8ce36","tid":321732,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"去熱刺"},{"pid":"1affc8b36ac371551e610aa45e768e2d62d27b60","tid":321732,"uid":10859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"加盟我轟對抗daddy"},{"pid":"053255319980cc4d116ac0cdc7c2888569480ec5","tid":321732,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"AC"},{"pid":"0d70a3861e33bbedd031bba3f4a30308c1acc8a2","tid":321732,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"重咩大宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢第隊波咋嘛"},{"pid":"dcfbeb85ba3f1dfa28c5bc3def8b6efc39edd2cd","tid":321732,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重咩大宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢第隊波咋嘛</blockquote><br />\n可以做教練呢"},{"pid":"fde2cb9269fdbed47a7cad077b103c8ec3c59e75","tid":321732,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:31:58.000Z","msg":"上年又咁玩，side9氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7285a19d97814b934518072a960164cb6c18ea64","tid":321732,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>重咩大宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/n